Class UrlStreamHandlers.ResolvingUrl

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.net.URLStreamHandler
      • io.github.ddimitrov.nuggets.UrlStreamHandlers.ResolvingUrl
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    UrlStreamHandlers.ResolversUrl
    Enclosing class:
    UrlStreamHandlers

    public abstract static class UrlStreamHandlers.ResolvingUrl
extends URLStreamHandler

    An URL stream handler that resolves to another URL schema - use this to build custom URL schemas that can shorten URIs or lookup resources.

    This class is abstract, so you may want to consider instead the UrlStreamHandlers.ResolversUrl, which uses lambda functions to resolve the resource.
